videos.description: Terance Mann drives to the hole with authority as he rises for a vicious slam.
videos.headline: Mann hammers down vicious jam

videos.description: Florida State's Mfiondu Kabengele protects the rim as he gets up for a sick block.
videos.headline: Kabengele elevates for nasty block

videos.description: M.J. Walker lobs it high to Christ Koumadje who throws down a monster alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Koumadje throws down alley-oop slam

videos.description: Notre Dame turns good defense into easy offense as Prentiss Hubb comes up with the steal and throws a dime to TJ Gibbs for an easy lay-in.
videos.headline: Hubb's full-court dime to Gibbs leads to easy lay-in

videos.description: John Mooney rises up through contact for a powerful two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Mooney slams home 2-handed flush
